Phenology and voltinism.
We have collected leaf mines in late March (
Florida
), mid-June (
North Carolina
), mid-July (
Oklahoma
), and mid- to late August (
Massachusetts and New York
), with adults emerging within a few weeks in each case (
Eiseman & Lonsdale 2018
).

Distribution.
USA
: DE, FL, GA, IA, ID, IL, [KS], *MA, MD, MI, MS, *NC, NY, OH, *OK, PA, SC, SD, TX, VA, [WI], WV; 
Canada
: AB, NL, ON, QC; 
Bermuda
; 
Bolivia
; 
Brazil
; 
Dominica
; 
Dominican Republic
; 
Guadeloupe
; 
Martinique
.
